The Telegraph - Calcutta
		 Tuesday, January 07, 2003 				 Minister calls for review
																								Guna: Union sports minister VikramVerma, called for a review of the Indian cricket teams run of embarrassing defeats on the ongoing tour of New Zealand.																								Cricket is a game of uncertainties, but there is a need to find out why all batsmen failed in New Zealand, the minister said on Monday. (PTI)
